OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FThe centuries old process of the papal
OL,6,Fconclave - the election of a new Pope
OL,7,F- is underway following the death of
OL,8,FPope Francis.
OL,10,FThe election of a new pope is a
OL,11,Fspecial moment, the Vatican City will
OL,12,Fbe full of anticipation as crowds
OL,13,Fgather outside St Peter's Square
OL,14,Fwaiting for the signal that the
OL,15,Fmonumental decision has been made.
OL,17,FInside the Sistine Chapel, behind
OL,18,Fmarble walls and beneath
OL,19,FMichelangelo's frescoes, 120 cardinals
OL,20,Fwill gather in red robes to select the
OL,21,Fnext pope with a historic vote.
