OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FWith no phones or connection to the
OL,6,Foutside world - the cardinals are
OL,7,Fguided only by centuries of tradition
OL,8,Fand faith.
OL,10,FHere, ITV News explains how a pope is
OL,11,Felected and when the new pontiff will
OL,12,Fbe announced.
OL,14,FWhat is the conclave?
OL,16,FFor centuries, leaders of the Roman
OL,17,FCatholic Church have been chosen at
OL,18,Fthe Vatican in private gatherings
OL,19,Fknown as conclaves.
