OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FOnce a candidate has been chosen, they
OL,6,Fare called to the front of the chapel
OL,7,Fand asked whether they are willing to
OL,8,Faccept.
OL,10,FIf the answer is yes, the new pope is
OL,11,Fthen asked to choose his new papal
OL,12,Fname.
OL,14,FThere are no rules around selecting
OL,15,Fthe papal name, however the name
OL,16,Fchosen by the Pope often reflects a
OL,17,Fpredecessor they admire or is linked
OL,18,Fto a revered saint, and can signify
OL,19,Fthe values they will focus on.
OL,21,FWhen is the new pope announced?
