OL,3,CConclave: How is a new Pope elected?
OL,5,FAfter each round of voting, the
OL,6,Fballots are burned with chemicals to
OL,7,Fmake the smoke either black - meaning
OL,8,Fno decision has been reached or white
OL,9,F- signalling a pope has been elected.
OL,11,FShortly after, the new pope - dressed
OL,12,Fin his new white robe and red slippers
OL,13,F- will appear from the main balcony of
OL,14,FSt Peter's Basilica.
